OL,5, Italy has become the latest country to 
OL,6, impose mandatory Covid tests on Chinese
OL,7, tourists, after China announced it     
OL,8, would reopen its borders next week.    
OL,10,FTighter measures have also been brought
OL,11,Fin by Japan, Malaysia, Taiwan and India
OL,12,F- while the US said it is considering  
OL,13,Fimposing more rules.                   
OL,15,FAfter almost three years of            
OL,16,Frestrictions, China will let people    
OL,17,Ftravel more easily from 8 January.     
OL,19,FAt the same time, the country is facing
OL,20,Fa surge in Covid cases.                
